= Silangkong = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Yorisyang ka alang Silangkong. 290 sapah ka kneego na sapah, 834 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnposo seejiq o mangal 30% niqan 249 hiyi sp, rahoq na oxay tnposo seejiq o mangal 70% niqan 585 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis15%, Bonon2%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq1%, ni rahoq na o1%.
